PrecisOrder authorizing the trips made by Mr. RON MacDONALD, M.P., to Vancouver, from February 10 to February 13, 1994, and to Boston on March 14, 1994, for the purpose of attending both the United Nations Conference on Straddling Fish Stocks and Highly Migratory Fish Stocks, and the Boston Seafood Show, in order to enhance his knowledge of the fisheries.
